    • Constructor Detail

      • Player

        public Player(java.lang.String name,
              int playerId,
              CatanColor color)
        Parameters:
        name - - Name of player
        playerId - - id for the game to reference for game order
        color - - Color to represent the player on the board.
        Precondition:
        name must be a non empty or null String, playerId must be between 0-3 and be unique other players in the game. Color must also be unique to other players in the game
        Postcondition:
        A player with the default setting will be created with the given name, playerId and color.
